  "prompt": "Which are the best 3 and 4 star hotels in Goa?",
  "response": "Goa is a popular tourist destination known for its beautiful beaches, vibrant nightlife, and rich cultural heritage. Here are some of the best 3-star and 4-star hotels in Goa that offer great hospitality and services:\n\n### **Best 3-Star Hotels in Goa**\n\n1. **Vivanta Goa, Panaji**\n   - **Location:** Panaji (Panjim)\n   - **Highlights:** Centrally located, modern amenities, rooftop pool, and excellent dining options.\n   - **Why Stay:** Great value for money, close to major attractions, and provides a comfortable stay.\n\n2. **Casa Vagator**\n   - **Location:** Vagator\n   - **Highlights:** Stylish rooms, close to Vagator Beach, vibrant atmosphere, and a good restaurant.\n   - **Why Stay:** Perfect for budget travelers looking for a mix of comfort and vibrant Goa vibes.\n\n3. **Riva Beach Resort**\n   - **Location:** Calangute\n   - **Highlights:** Beachfront location, spacious rooms, outdoor pool, and a relaxed ambiance.\n   - **Why Stay:** Ideal for families and couples looking to enjoy the beach and a laid-back environment.\n\n### **Best 4-Star Hotels in Goa**\n\n1. **Grand Hyatt Goa**\n   - **Location:** Bambolim\n   - **Highlights:** Luxurious rooms, multiple dining options, large swimming pool, and private beach access.\n   - **Why Stay:** Offers a premium experience with top-notch amenities and a serene environment.\n\n2. **Kenilworth Resort & Spa**\n   - **Location:** Utorda\n   - **Highlights:** Beachfront property, spa services, fine dining, and well-appointed rooms.\n   - **Why Stay:** Perfect for those seeking a luxurious yet tranquil beachfront retreat.\n\n3. **Novotel Goa Resort & Spa**\n   - **Location:** Candolim\n   - **Highlights:** Contemporary design, family-friendly amenities, spa, and multiple swimming pools.\n   - **Why Stay:** Great for families and couples looking for a comfortable and stylish stay with excellent services.\n\nThese hotels are well-regarded for their hospitality, cleanliness,",
  "temperature": 1.0,
